The dreidel tells you the overall theme of the holiday and the rules of the game: 

"A great miracle happened there" = Nes Gadol Haya Sham. 

Nes (nun, nothing happens); 
Gadol (gimmel, take all); 
Haya (hey, take half); 
Sham (shin, put in one). 

Loved this theme. 

